But we have not found such differences in the CERN so far.
Impacts
The impact of such investigations on our day-to-day lives is difficult to predict, but we do not believe that we are wrong to say that you will have any.
For you to see: in the early 1960s, laser pioneers in laboratories did not at all suspect the revolution that their work would provoke.
