On the other hand, typical Hollywood scenes a little lighter, marked by irony and a slight exaggeration.
And in addition, scenes from the CIA headquarters and other institutions: brought men who analyze the situation at the negotiating table, in the hallways of the office, by phone...
Ben Affleck has managed to restart his career in an excellent way.
