The architecture study MVRDV shows that the real adventures are not only in the head - in the example of the library of Spijkenisse and the newly finished "book pile"- 2 photos
"I think the building is fun, it has a futuristic look, and finally there's something interesting to see," says Lisette Verhaig, a passerby passing through the street.
