Impersonators simply add a couple of letters to be able to record their marks.
In this way, Gucci becomes Lu-Gucci and instead of Prada is registered Prada-Kny.
German companies are also legally copied in the same way, as has happened to the manufacturer of Puma sports items.
Pattloch opens an archive where he keeps seats from Beijing's brand office.
